headline: Escalating US-China Trade War to Hurt These Tech Stocks in 2025

headline: Escalating US-China Trade War to Hurt These Stocks in 2025
summary: After Trump threatens 60% China tariffs and Beijing bans rare minerals, top chipmakers AMD, INTC, MU, QCOM and ASML face major risks in 2025.
